value.value: Embryonic cell of lineage ABpraapppp fuses into embryonic large hypodermal syncytium hyp7.

definition.value: In Sulston et al., 1983, probably this cell is referred to as MSpappal. In the movie published by Richards, et al., 2013, it appears that the anterior daughter of MSpappa (MSpappaa) ends up on the left of MSpappap.
